==Japanese==
===Noun===
'''四つ''' ([[よっつ]], ''yottsu'')

# [[four]] things [small or without a counter category]
#: 四つ (よっつ, ''yottsu'') is only used when the items counted have no specific counter category. See [[w:Japanese counter word|Wikipedia's "Japanese counter word" entry]] for details.

